title: GSP#4 - Ghost Slash Proposal
body:
Minimum stake deposit Total Slash Proposal of the protocol agent yCMHR.

**Motivations**
- The protocol agent apparently abandoned the project for a period longer than 1 month and without notice.
- The agent is not attending scheduled meetings
- The agent is not performing requested tasks
- The agent is not able to contribute to the project anymore.

Please, vote YES to approve or NO to decline the proposal.
